tool_description: Efficient and user-friendly Instagram API with outstanding performance. Achieve 99.99% uptime and access any Instagram data. Customizable API plans and additional features available upon request.
title: Instagram API Cheap and Fast

api_list.name: Instagram profile by ID
api_list.description: get a user's profile by their id
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://instagram-api-cheap-and-fast.p.rapidapi.com/profile/{id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "instagram-api-cheap-and-fast.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
